16#include <inttypes.h>

19#include <isc/mem.h>

23#include <dns/ipkeylist.h>

26void
27dns_ipkeylist_init(dns_ipkeylist_t *ipkl) {
28 ipkl->count = 0;
29 ipkl->allocated = 0;
30 ipkl->addrs = NULL;
31 ipkl->dscps = NULL;
32 ipkl->keys = NULL;
33 ipkl->labels = NULL;
34}
35
36void
37dns_ipkeylist_clear(isc_mem_t *mctx, dns_ipkeylist_t *ipkl) {
38 uint32_t i;
39
40 REQUIRE(ipkl != NULL);
41
42 if (ipkl->allocated == 0)
43 return;
44
45 if (ipkl->addrs != NULL)
46 isc_mem_put(mctx, ipkl->addrs,
47 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(isc_sockaddr_t));
48
49 if (ipkl->dscps != NULL)
50 isc_mem_put(mctx, ipkl->dscps,
51 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(isc_dscp_t));
52
53 if (ipkl->keys != NULL) {
54 for (i = 0; i < ipkl->allocated; i++) {
55 if (ipkl->keys[i] == NULL)
56 continue;
57 if (dns_name_dynamic(ipkl->keys[i]))
58 dns_name_free(ipkl->keys[i], mctx);
59 isc_mem_put(mctx, ipkl->keys[i], sizeof(dns_name_t));
60 }
61 isc_mem_put(mctx, ipkl->keys,
62 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
63 }
64
65 if (ipkl->labels != NULL) {
66 for (i = 0; i < ipkl->allocated; i++) {
67 if (ipkl->labels[i] == NULL)
68 continue;
69 if (dns_name_dynamic(ipkl->labels[i]))
70 dns_name_free(ipkl->labels[i], mctx);
71 isc_mem_put(mctx, ipkl->labels[i], sizeof(dns_name_t));
72 }
73 isc_mem_put(mctx, ipkl->labels,
74 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
75 }
76
77 dns_ipkeylist_init(ipkl);
78}
79
80isc_result_t
81dns_ipkeylist_copy(isc_mem_t *mctx, const dns_ipkeylist_t *src,
82 dns_ipkeylist_t *dst)
83{
84 isc_result_t result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
85 uint32_t i;
86
87 REQUIRE(dst != NULL);
88 /* dst might be preallocated, we don't care, but it must be empty */
89 REQUIRE(dst->count == 0);
90
91 if (src->count == 0)
92 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
93
94 result = dns_ipkeylist_resize(mctx, dst, src->count);
95 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
96 return (result);
97
98 memmove(dst->addrs, src->addrs, src->count * sizeof(isc_sockaddr_t));
99
100 if (src->dscps != NULL) {
101 memmove(dst->dscps, src->dscps,
102 src->count * sizeof(isc_dscp_t));
103 }
104
105 if (src->keys != NULL) {
106 for (i = 0; i < src->count; i++) {
107 if (src->keys[i] != NULL) {
108 dst->keys[i] = isc_mem_get(mctx,
109 sizeof(dns_name_t));
110 if (dst->keys[i] == NULL) {
111 result = ISC_R_NOMEMORY;
112 goto cleanup_keys;
113 }
114 dns_name_init(dst->keys[i], NULL);
115 result = dns_name_dup(src->keys[i], mctx,
116 dst->keys[i]);
117 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
118 goto cleanup_keys;
119 } else {
120 dst->keys[i] = NULL;
121 }
122 }
123 }
124
125 if (src->labels != NULL) {
126 for (i = 0; i < src->count; i++) {
127 if (src->labels[i] != NULL) {
128 dst->labels[i] = isc_mem_get(mctx,
129 sizeof(dns_name_t));
130 if (dst->labels[i] == NULL) {
131 result = ISC_R_NOMEMORY;
132 goto cleanup_labels;
133 }
134 dns_name_init(dst->labels[i], NULL);
135 result = dns_name_dup(src->labels[i], mctx,
136 dst->labels[i]);
137 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
138 goto cleanup_labels;
139 } else {
140 dst->labels[i] = NULL;
141 }
142 }
143 }
144 dst->count = src->count;
145 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
146
147 cleanup_labels:
148 do {
149 if (dst->labels[i] != NULL) {
150 if (dns_name_dynamic(dst->labels[i]))
151 dns_name_free(dst->labels[i], mctx);
152 isc_mem_put(mctx, dst->labels[i], sizeof(dns_name_t));
153 dst->labels[i] = NULL;
154 }
155 } while (i-- > 0);
156
157 cleanup_keys:
158 do {
159 if (dst->keys[i] != NULL) {
160 if (dns_name_dynamic(dst->keys[i]))
161 dns_name_free(dst->keys[i], mctx);
162 isc_mem_put(mctx, dst->keys[i], sizeof(dns_name_t));
163 dst->keys[i] = NULL;
164 }
165 } while (i-- > 0);
166
167 return (result);
168}
169
170isc_result_t
171dns_ipkeylist_resize(isc_mem_t *mctx, dns_ipkeylist_t *ipkl, unsigned int n) {
172 isc_sockaddr_t *addrs = NULL;
173 isc_dscp_t *dscps = NULL;
174 dns_name_t **keys = NULL;
175 dns_name_t **labels = NULL;
176
177 REQUIRE(ipkl != NULL);
178 REQUIRE(n > ipkl->count);
179
180 if (n <= ipkl->allocated)
181 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
182
183 addrs = isc_mem_get(mctx, n * sizeof(isc_sockaddr_t));
184 if (addrs == NULL)
185 goto nomemory;
186 dscps = isc_mem_get(mctx, n * sizeof(isc_dscp_t));
187 if (dscps == NULL)
188 goto nomemory;
189 keys = isc_mem_get(mctx, n * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
190 if (keys == NULL)
191 goto nomemory;
192 labels = isc_mem_get(mctx, n * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
193 if (labels == NULL)
194 goto nomemory;
195
196 if (ipkl->addrs != NULL) {
197 memmove(addrs, ipkl->addrs,
198 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(isc_sockaddr_t));
199 isc_mem_put(mctx, ipkl->addrs,
200 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(isc_sockaddr_t));
201 }
202 ipkl->addrs = addrs;
203 memset(&ipkl->addrs[ipkl->allocated], 0,
204 (n - ipkl->allocated) * sizeof(isc_sockaddr_t));
205
206 if (ipkl->dscps != NULL) {
207 memmove(dscps, ipkl->dscps,
208 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(isc_dscp_t));
209 isc_mem_put(mctx, ipkl->dscps,
210 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(isc_dscp_t));
211 }
212 ipkl->dscps = dscps;
213 memset(&ipkl->dscps[ipkl->allocated], 0,
214 (n - ipkl->allocated) * sizeof(isc_dscp_t));
215
216 if (ipkl->keys) {
217 memmove(keys, ipkl->keys,
218 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
219 isc_mem_put(mctx, ipkl->keys,
220 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
221 }
222 ipkl->keys = keys;
223 memset(&ipkl->keys[ipkl->allocated], 0,
224 (n - ipkl->allocated) * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
225
226 if (ipkl->labels != NULL) {
227 memmove(labels, ipkl->labels,
228 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
229 isc_mem_put(mctx, ipkl->labels,
230 ipkl->allocated * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
231 }
232 ipkl->labels = labels;
233 memset(&ipkl->labels[ipkl->allocated], 0,
234 (n - ipkl->allocated) * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
235
236 ipkl->allocated = n;
237 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
238
239nomemory:
240 if (addrs != NULL)
241 isc_mem_put(mctx, addrs, n * sizeof(isc_sockaddr_t));
242 if (dscps != NULL)
243 isc_mem_put(mctx, dscps, n * sizeof(isc_dscp_t));
244 if (keys != NULL)
245 isc_mem_put(mctx, keys, n * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
246 if (labels != NULL)
247 isc_mem_put(mctx, labels, n * sizeof(dns_name_t *));
248
249 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
250}
